				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I'd have to say yes.  I went to the Basilisk caves solo and made 4.5 yellows (straight to 40) in 3 hours and 41 in 3.5 hours.  I used 39 Fire pet with Phantom Plate, 2 Dagger of Symbols and BO2.  Pull with Malise, heal pet at 70%, Cinder Bolt and loot.  6 min or so respawns.  By the time I killed 4th one, 1st one respawned so it was constant killing.  Loot was eggs, meat and poison sacs.  Great exp, poor loot (unless your learning Baking tradeskill).  Group of mid 20s to low 30s would level fast here.<br><br>Give it a go and see if you like it.  Quite empty on Xegony save for the rangers outside fear kiting Griffons.<br><br> <p>Durell Spiritseer, 55 Templar<BR>Kaldara Spiritblade, 46 Warrior<BR>Zisambas, 33 Mage<BR>Proud Officer of Defenders of Fae<BR></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/udurellspiritseer.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Durell Spiritseer</A> at: 8/21/02 7:04:19 am<br></i></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
