				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">You could work Tundra Yeti's in NW corner of DL to 44.  Seven spawns and you can hold entire cave if you 1) have a horse, 2) have a C3, or 3) sit and med while pet is fighting.  I'm not sure how the xp's will compare - the Tundra Yeti's should all con blue at 43, but they are on a 22 minute timer while those basilisks seem to be on a (at most) 6 minute timer.  I think around 43 I was getting two blues per 7 Yetis - not great, but usually beat the &quot;running around busting your hump always looking over your shoulder for adds routine&quot;.  You could also work the Hulking Golras in Timorous Deep - 3 spawn on a 12 minute timer.  Biggest downside is that Halara will occasionally replace one of the regular hulkings and it was a tough battle with her until I got the 44 pets. <p></p><i></i></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
