				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The cave basilisks are a decent camp.  I finished 75% of 40 and into 10% of 41 doing this camp.  The great thing is the constant spawn and minimal downtime.  By the time you finish the last basilisk, the first has respawned.<br><br>Key is minimizing mana loss.  Med a lot, and get KEI if you can.  I used El Zippo, and the mobs were burned quite nice against the DS.  Throw in a couple heals and nuke (shock of spikes) at the end for xp.  For a focused fire pet with plate and 2 sword of runes, it was a cake walk.<br><br>1-3% per kill. <p></p><i></i></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
